QuantumForge 2.0.0
==================

The authoritative project overview, capability matrix, installation links, and
scientific-status warnings are in README.md.

IMPORTANT: several source packages are experimental or disconnected prototypes;
they are not complete VASP, CASTEP, thermo_pw, phonopy, BoltzTraP2, GNN, or
advanced-physics workflows. See docs/CODE_AUDIT.md before research use.

License terms are in LICENSE. The previous Apache-license statement in this file
conflicted with the repository LICENSE and has been removed; third-party and
upstream notices are recorded in THIRD_PARTY_NOTICES.md.
